96
00:06:18,890 --> 00:06:23,360
A calzone is pizza dough folded in half and stuffed with a filling.

97
00:06:23,710 --> 00:06:27,820
They can be baked or fried and can be found in a variety of forms throughout Italy.

98
00:06:28,110 --> 00:06:33,120
They typically contain mozzarella cheese and other pizza toppings, don't they?

99
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,740
That means...

100
00:06:34,740 --> 00:06:35,720
Ah!

101
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:37,290
There's curry inside!

102
00:06:37,290 --> 00:06:40,170
So this is something like 
an Italian version of curry bread?

103
00:06:41,710 --> 00:06:45,090
It's rather different from the previous dishes we've had. Very interesting!

104
00:06:45,090 --> 00:06:46,760
Well, let's dig in.

105
00:06:48,550 --> 00:06:50,050
Splash!

106
00:06:50,300 --> 00:06:52,140
T-Tomatoes?

107
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:56,600
The curry's overflowing with the rich, 
juicy flavor of tomatoes!

108
00:06:56,970 --> 00:07:00,980
Inside the calzone is a curry that was made primarily with tomatoes.

109
00:07:01,270 --> 00:07:05,440
Oh, you didn't add stock or
any other liquids to the curry?

110
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,650
Right.

111
00:07:06,650 --> 00:07:09,650
If you heat tightly packed tomatoes
at the bottom of a pot,

112
00:07:09,650 --> 00:07:11,910
they release a surprising amount of liquid.

113
00:07:12,570 --> 00:07:16,580
I added a special spice mix that pairs well with the tomatoes' acidity.

114
00:07:16,580 --> 00:07:20,920
It resulted in a rich curry that's
 full of the tomato's umami.

115
00:07:21,250 --> 00:07:22,380
As for the dough,

116
00:07:22,380 --> 00:07:24,920
I used the grape yeast our family makes.

117
00:07:25,170 --> 00:07:26,670
<i>The surface is so light and crisp!</i>

118
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:29,090
<i>Yet when you bite into it, it's chewy and sweet.</i>

119
00:07:29,380 --> 00:07:32,430
<i>It's a perfect match for the rich curry.</i>

120
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:34,220
Wonderful!

121
00:07:34,220 --> 00:07:36,590
You re-imagined curry bread as Italian cuisine

122
00:07:36,590 --> 00:07:38,810
