completely new in the process!

123
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:45,560
<i>"The pitiable younger brother, forever doomed to sit in the shadow cast by his older brother."</i>

124
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:48,820
<i>Many have thought of Isami Aldini that way.</i>

125
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:51,530
<i>But that's not the truth.</i>

126
00:07:51,530 --> 00:07:54,950
<i>He too is an explorer in a foreign land,</i>

127
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:57,080
