172
00:09:52,020 --> 00:09:53,190
I see!

173
00:09:53,190 --> 00:09:57,680
The tamari soy sauce and Parmesan
 combine to create this much depth.

174
00:09:57,680 --> 00:10:00,870
S-Still, with the cheese in the dough,

175
00:10:00,870 --> 00:10:02,460
the heat from boiling the pasta wouldâ€”

