179
00:10:10,130 --> 00:10:14,050
<i>The curry sauce's depth of flavor is enhanced by the tamari soy sauce.</i>

180
00:10:14,050 --> 00:10:15,880
<i>And when you bite into it,</i>

181
00:10:15,880 --> 00:10:19,340
<i>the rich flavor of the Parmesan cheese spreads in your mouth, delivering a final blow!</i>

182
00:10:19,800 --> 00:10:23,310
<i>Marinating cream cheese in soy sauce is a well-known technique,</i>

183
00:10:23,310 --> 00:10:27,060
<i>but who would've guessed that Parmesan and tamari soy sauce would pair so well?</i>

184
00:10:27,310 --> 00:10:33,570
Italian and Japanese cuisine have achieved a new harmony within the format of this curry dish!

185
00:10:37,070 --> 00:10:38,650
Takumi Aldini...

186
