He is yet another pioneer of the culinary world!

187
00:10:46,380 --> 00:10:48,010
<i>They're both skilled chefs,</i>

188
00:10:48,010 --> 00:10:49,830
<i>but maybe Takumi is a tad more sophisticated.</i>

189
00:10:50,330 --> 00:10:54,550
