<i>Bro, I'm sorry.</i>

196
00:11:14,270 --> 00:11:16,820
<i>I ruined your cooking.</i>

197
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:20,070
<i>I wanted to show them that I'm just as good.</i>

198
00:11:20,700 --> 00:11:23,570
<i>I didn't want to become a burden to Takumi.</i>

199
00:11:23,870 --> 00:11:24,830
<i>Mezzaluna...</i>

200
00:11:25,780 --> 00:11:28,370
<i>The blade named for the half-moon.</i>

201
00:11:28,370 --> 00:11:30,710
<i>Don't you think it's perfect for us?</i>

202
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:37,050
<i>When two halves of a whole come together, 
perfection is born.</i>

203
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:41,380
<i>Aldini needs both of us, Isami!</i>

204
00:11:41,890 --> 00:11:45,140
<i>I will move forward with every step you take.</i>

205
00:11:45,640 --> 00:11:51,730
<i>One day, our restaurant will
 become the best in all of Italy!</i>

206
