207
00:11:53,850 --> 00:11:55,860
<i>Welcome to Trattoria Aldini!</i>

208
00:11:56,110 --> 00:11:57,980
<i>Ciao, Aldini brothers!</i>

209
00:11:57,980 --> 00:11:59,610
<i>Let us have the best possible meal today too!</i>

210
00:11:59,610 --> 00:12:00,570
<i>We're counting on you!</i>

211
00:12:01,570 --> 00:12:04,410
<i>He's an everyday sort of guy you can always tease,</i>

212
00:12:04,410 --> 00:12:07,670
<i>but he becomes a totally different person once he puts on his chef's coat.</i>

213
